{"tid":1322533,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家放過香蕉糖啦","createTime":"2019-07-16T03:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T06:17:34.000Z","uid":3028,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"aeccb8535a28a4c2654235a552f498323dbf95f1","tid":1322533,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:18:44.000Z","msg":"香蕉糖只不過係條甩頭髮既垃圾<br />\n唔值得花咁多時間晌佢身上<br />\n<br />\n相反栢林狗條撚樣濫用私刑<br />\n搞到手足殘廢<br />\n條撚樣命水咁好<br />\n細個人見人愛<br />\n成世人一帆風順<br />\n三十出頭就總督察<br />\n十皮一個月做下樣咪算囉<br />\n仲要衝出黎搏上位<br />\n俾依d人上到以後一定後患無窮<br />\n<br />\n再者依家八十前比較撐警果班一定識佢<br />\n搵佢做文宣效果一定好<br />\n俾班廢老知道<br />\n天真無邪既細路入左警隊<br />\n都只會腐化變左惡魔<br />\n從而了解到警隊已經腐敗到無得救<br />\n<br />\n集中火力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bb6bc9c808e6ffaee0ef9baade7c2dd70f016f4","tid":1322533,"uid":268920,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:22:36.000Z","msg":"撚香蕉糖同搞柏林狗冇衝突 可同時執行"},{"pid":"a708f85de763d4273bc5ec22fe489d873a60aca4","tid":1322533,"uid":214880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"去旅行既巴絲可以幫手去外國表揚英勇警員"},{"pid":"486606ddc5e78be37a07d4c1306be95bcc92766b","tid":1322533,"uid":261915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:38:43.000Z","msg":"Wave sir哩? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46acfc60035160b9ece4338356c5de756c6bcd03","tid":1322533,"uid":125680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:39:48.000Z","msg":"連登名言why not both都唔識？"},{"pid":"46fd339e5d30ed9c29502b858b29877b43513758","tid":1322533,"uid":30503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T03:42:31.000Z","msg":"其實有用架，，打擊班犬氣焰，等同精神攻擊，長期受壓情況下，佢地會好迷茫，分分鐘精神病"},{"pid":"ac7949b7122e5f835f3baf1998b86e09c1e5bb92","tid":1322533,"uid":3028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\